import React from 'react'
import axios from 'axios'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'

import App from './App'

axios
	.get("http://localhost:3001/notes")
	.then(response => {
		const notes = response.data
		console.log(notes)})

ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(<App />)
